description:
Danny welcomes the newest addition to Bravo's Real Housewives of New Jersey, the beautiful Margaret Josephs, to the show. They talk about the new season, her iconic pigtails, Mariah Carey, and her feud with Siggy. Danny also breaks down #RHOD, #RHOC, and Hallmark holiday movies. PS if you're just here for the Margaret interview, it starts at the 12 minute mark. ;) 

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
